This paper focuses on the impact of design on partner models and subsequent effects on interaction in human-machine dialogue. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), software engineering (cs.SD), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
